The heady spice aromas & the tantalizing flavors of Kerala cuisine is what makes this state every food lover’s paradise. From Mappila community fare, to elaborate sadyas to lip-smacking Syrian Christian dishes to a steady supply of seafood delights, Kerala has a multitude of both vegetarian & non vegetarian options. Raviz Group of hotels in Kerala offers authentic Kerala specialties prepared the traditional way along with continental fare.
